title: AAVE or SUSHI? You decide.
body:
Last week we launched stake COMP, earn CAKE along with a COMP-ETH pool. 

This week we’re proposing to launch either:

1. **Stake AAVE, earn CAKE** + a 1x AAVE-ETH pool.

Or 

2. **Stake SUSHI, earn CAKE** + a 1x SUSHI-ETH pool.

Note that this is just an initial gauge of interest and there will be a final vote and announcement with the details of whichever option is shown to be the favourite.

So, which would you like to see on PancakeSwap?
author: 0x6eaf1b33b8672c5dc40aB8f4bA3A0111723126c7
